# No .DS_Store in Git

- **Do not stage or commit** any `.DS_Store` file. These are macOS folder view metadata and are not part of the project.
- Ensure **.DS_Store** is listed in the project’s **.gitignore**. When committing, ensure no .DS_Store files are included in the diff.
- If .DS_Store appears in a diff or `git status`, remove it from the index and add .DS_Store to .gitignore if missing.
